- Reject unsupported or AE-version-dependent mutations with normalized errors.\
5.3 Project Item Mutation Tools\
New Tools\
- create-folder\
- move-item-to-folder\
- replace-footage\
- reload-footage\
- set-proxy\
- clear-proxy\
