5.4 Selection Tools\
New Tools\
- get-selected-layers\
- select-layers\
- clear-selection\
Rules\
- Every mutation tool should be tagged conceptually as one of:\
  - safe\
  - destructive\
  - version-dependent\
- Every mutation should use undo grouping where possible.\
- Every response should include exact targets that were changed.\
Acceptance Criteria\
- An LLM can inspect -> mutate -> verify with explicit identifiers at each step.\
- Destructive vs safe operations are documented and machine-readable.\
