PHASE 10 - Migration and Rollout\
--------------------------------------------------\
Purpose\
Ship iteratively without breaking current users.\
Rollout Sequence\
1. Introduce contracts and diagnostics without behavior changes where possible.\
2. Add new introspection tools first.\
3. Add write tools based on the new contracts.\
4. Migrate old tools gradually to normalized responses.\
5. Keep legacy aliases documented as compatibility forms.\
6. Deprecate old response shapes only after clear documentation and adoption.\
Rules\
- Avoid large rewrites without intermediate checkpoints.\
- Prefer additive changes first.\
- Keep compatibility visible in docs.\
